.@meow expands stablecoin payment capabilities with BVNK

With BVNK's infrastructure, Meow customers will be able to access multiple stablecoins and crypto, convert to USD, and access blockchain and Swift rails – all from one platform.

@brandon CEO of Meow: "By partnering with BVNK we're giving customers a faster, lower-cost way to move money through a single platform."
